          "category": "correctness",
          "message": "The filter in `#getHighestCount` uses `created_at:<=` (inclusive of today) instead of `created_at:<` (exclusive of today), which may include today's emails in the highest count calculation. This could cause the warmup limit to be based on an incomplete day's data, potentially leading to an incorrect (lower) limit.",
